{"tid":1138024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角男子失聯多日　友人上門揭發吊頸亡","createTime":"2019-05-04T09:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T09:38:34.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3c5691ae809cfea92ef4a6aedb277a40670d9b","tid":1138024,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"旺角男子上吊亡。今午（4日）2時半，一名男子到旺角花園街83號9樓一單位，探訪一名失聯多日的男友人時，惟拍門無人應，而單位更傳出異味，擔心他發生事故報警求助。消防接報到場破門入屋，揭發男子在屋內上吊，昏迷不醒。救護員檢查後證實男子已明顯死亡，警方正在現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8ZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=d866bc8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190504/mobile/bkn-20190504155545863-0504_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190504%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190504155545863-0504_00822_001.html&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8ZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e6f9fc0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190504/mobile/bkn-20190504155545863-0504_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"11a58f51580754b74c5062b8f0cc45aeab645ac5","tid":1138024,"uid":810,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"乜撚野失聯呀"},{"pid":"661fee4a23fa5a363e17554e025b4e839247e4eb","tid":1138024,"uid":3852,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"失去聯絡就失去聯絡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2ea771b9b508775a777f086574dd15bc96ee8b","tid":11